  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To compare pyrimethamine and intravenous (IV) clindamycin vs. pyrimethamine and sulfonamides
      in the treatment of AIDS patients with central nervous system (CNS) Toxoplasma gondii.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
